OL,3,CChris Brown has request for bail
OL,4,Cdenied after 'bottle attack' court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FBrown, wearing a black T-shirt and
OL,8,Fblack Nike jogging bottoms, was
OL,9,Fflanked by two security guards in the
OL,10,Fdock.
OL,12,FHe confirmed his name was Christopher
OL,13,FMaurice Brown, provided his date of
OL,14,Fbirth and gave the Lowry Hotel as his
OL,15,Faddress.
OL,17,FBrown watched on intently as brief
OL,18,Fdetails of the case against him were
OL,19,Foutlined by prosecutor Hannah Nicholls.
