OL,3,CChris Brown has request for bail
OL,4,Cdenied after 'bottle attack' court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FMs Nicholls said the alleged victim
OL,8,Fwas stood at the bar of the Tape
OL,9,Fnightclub on February 19 2023 when the
OL,10,Fdefendant launched an "unprovoked
OL,11,Fattack" in which the complainant was
OL,12,Fstruck several times with a bottle.
OL,14,FShe said: "The defendant then pursued
OL,15,Fhim to a separate area of the
OL,16,Fnightclub where the victim was punched
OL,17,Fand kicked repeatedly by him and
OL,18,Fanother."
