OL,3,CChris Brown has request for bail
OL,4,Cdenied after 'bottle attack' court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FBrown confirmed to Judge Hirst that he
OL,8,Funderstood he had further been
OL,9,Fremanded in custody until next month.
OL,11,FThe singer nodded to an associate in
OL,12,Fthe front row of the court's public
OL,13,Fgallery as he was led from the dock
OL,14,Ffollowing the 30-minute hearing.
OL,16,FMembers of the public joined members
OL,17,Fof press to watch proceedings in Court
OL,18,F17, along with others following on
OL,19,Fvideolink in an overspill court.
