OL,3,CChris Brown has request for bail
OL,4,Cdenied after 'bottle attack' court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FBrown is said to have flown into
OL,8,FManchester Airport on a private jet on
OL,9,FWednesday afternoon in preparation for
OL,10,Ftour dates in UK in June and July.
OL,12,FHe was arrested at Manchester's Lowry
OL,13,FHotel at 2am on Thursday by detectives
OL,14,Ffrom the Metropolitan Police.
OL,16,FThe Go Crazy singer is set to tour the
OL,17,FUK in June and July, with dates at Co-
OL,18,FOp Live in Manchester and Principality
OL,19,FStadium in Cardiff.
